Endpoint Type: POST
Route: /auth
Type: "application/json"
Auth: No Auth Required
Description: When the endpoint is hit with correct username and password, 200 Status code and headers are supplied back with JWT Token.
Expected Format: {
    username: "hello@simple.com",
    password: "asimplepassword",
}
Success Code: 200
Success Response: {
    "status": "ok"
}
Success Headers: {
    "Authorization": "Bearer asudhausdbhasbfhasdbfhasbdfdsf",
}
Failure Code: 500
Failure Response: {}
Failure Headers: {}